		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Definitely - the difference isn't much on GB/GBC because the tunes are basically suqare waves with high harmonics - but on the GBA the difference is just unimaginable.
<br />
<br />My GBC has <em>really</em> crap sound trough the jack - probably a bad contact or something.
<br />
<br />I only figured halfway my Golden Sun 2 play-through I've been missing a good half of the soundtrack not hearing basslines at all - some other games suffer of this too but GS/GS2 is one of the most noticeable.
<br />That being said, the speakers in the GBA are quite noisy as well - it sounds like there is always wind in it.

		

